## 🔹 **6. Use `unordered_map` Instead of `map`**
```cpp
unordered_map<int, int> freq;
freq[5] = 10;
```
✅ **Effect**: `O(1)` average time complexity vs `O(log n)` in `map`.

💡 **Use `map` if you need sorted keys.**

