## 🔹 **7. Use `priority_queue` for Min/Max**
```cpp
priority_queue<int> maxHeap; // Default max-heap
priority_queue<int, vector<int>, greater<int>> minHeap; // Min-heap
```
✅ **Effect**: Handles max/min elements efficiently in `O(log n)`.

