## 🔹 **11. Use Bit Manipulation for Speed**
Check if a number is power of 2:
```cpp
bool isPowerOf2(int x) { return x && !(x & (x - 1)); }
```
Count set bits:
```cpp
int countBits(int n) { return __builtin_popcount(n); }
```
Find first set bit:
```cpp
int firstSetBit(int n) { return __builtin_ctz(n); }
```
✅ **Effect**: Faster than loops.

